// Build configuration for the PoseDeck app.
//
// API_BASE_URL is the base URL of the PocketBase backend. It is surfaced into
// Info.plist (key `APIBaseURL` via $(API_BASE_URL)) and read at runtime by
// AppConfig.apiBaseURL.
//
// NOTE: xcconfig treats `//` as a comment everywhere, including inside values.
// A bare `http://localhost:8090` would have everything from the `//` stripped,
// yielding `http:`. Work around this by splitting the scheme's slashes into a
// separate variable and recombining — a standard xcconfig idiom.
SLASH = /
API_BASE_URL = http:$(SLASH)$(SLASH)localhost:8090

// To point at a LAN backend (e.g. TrueNAS), override locally, e.g.:
//   API_BASE_URL = http:$(SLASH)$(SLASH)192.168.1.50:8090
